E[grp-jr] t=concept n=subgroup-junior
---
Q[n] =1240 u n=sample-size
Q[period] =6 mo
Q[eff-main] ~=32 pct n=efficiency-gain-intervention
Q[eff-sr] ~=41 pct n=efficiency-gain-senior
Q[eff-jr] ~=21 pct n=efficiency-gain-junior
